column7: This enemy is just excited to be here.
The tower's elite robot security force. Can't move or attack diagonally.
Likes to hedge their bets by attacking multiple spaces at once. Not concerned about hitting co-workers.
Wields two weapons. One weapon is aimed at you. The other one, who knows.
Long range attacker. You probably need to stand back further than you think.
Able to attack in water. Wields a three-pronged weapon.
Frankly it’s a miracle they haven't hit themselves yet.
column8: Wields nunchuck, which is a silly weapon in this game

column7: Your nemesis, in the flesh at last!
Cautious and sneaky. Doesn't like a fair fight.
A training dummy. Does no attacks.
A training dummy, blindly attacking with a real weapon. What could go wrong?
A moving target to test your hand-eye co-ordination.
